---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Team Lists 1888–1980 · Wallaroo FC"
  description="The Wallaroo Football Club team-list archive — every recorded A Grade line-up from 1888 to 1980, transcribed from newspaper reports and club budgets. The full source document, page by page."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Team-List Archive"
    title="Every recorded line-up,"
    titleItalic="1888 to 1980."
    intro="Ninety-two years of A Grade team sheets, scanned from newspapers and club budgets. The archive that carries the club forward into the modern era where our current games-tally begins."
  />

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="eyebrow">A note from the Historian</div>
      <blockquote class="note">
        Teamlists dating back to the 1880s through to 1980, where the current games tally
        was started. This was recorded from the newspapers, much like the other documents.
        As such, I can't guarantee accuracy.
        <br /><br />
        Also, primarily only A Grade was listed. I can't be sure it lists every game everyone
        played, because the information comes from the papers (and later, budgets), so games
        may be missing and it may favour goalkickers and best players.
        <br /><br />
        A hard copy can be read at the club.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="archive">
    <div class="container wide">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Archive</div>
      <h2>Ninety-two years <span class="ital">of Bulldogs.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede">
        The archive spans <strong>1888 to 1980</strong> — the point at which the club's current
        games-played tally begins. From the earliest Yorke Peninsula Football Association
        line-ups on rutted country ovals, through two World Wars, the mining decline, and the
        first Bulldog premierships. Every scanned page is preserved below.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/history/team-lists-1888-1980.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Open the archive
        </a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/history/team-lists-1888-1980.pdf" download>
          Download PDF (22.6 MB)
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="viewer">
        <iframe
          src="/history/team-lists-1888-1980.pdf#toolbar=1&navpanes=0"
          title="Wallaroo FC Team Lists 1888–1980"
          loading="lazy"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="closing">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="eyebrow">Beyond 1980</div>
      <h3>The modern games register.</h3>
      <p>
        From 1980 onward the club maintains a full games-played register, and the two
        Bulldogs at the head of the pack are <strong>Darren Smith (390 games)</strong> and
        <strong>Lindsay Smith (312 games)</strong>. Both feature on our
        <a href="/history">150 Games Club board</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Older reports, photographs and jumpers not in this document sit at the clubrooms —
        contact the Historian <strong>Michael West</strong> via
        <a href="mailto:admin@wallaroofc.com.au">admin@wallaroofc.com.au</a> to make an
        appointment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .container { margin: 0 auto; }
  .container.wide   { max-width: 1200px; }
  .container.narrow { max-width: 780px; }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--headline); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--red); margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 3px; background: var(--red); }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 56px);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  h2 .ital {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--red);
    text-transform: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  h3 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 38px);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }

  .lede {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  /* ── Intro / historian note ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .intro { background: var(--cream); padding: 72px 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .note {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--white);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(10, 31, 61, 0.05);
  }

  /* ── Archive with embedded viewer ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .archive { background: var(--white); padding: 80px 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 8px 0 40px; }
  .btn {
    font-family: var(--headline);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn.primary {
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--red);
  }
  .btn.primary:hover { background: var(--red-deep); border-color: var(--red-deep); }
  .btn.ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    border: 2px solid var(--blue-deep);
  }
  .btn.ghost:hover { background: var(--blue-deep); color: var(--white); }

  .viewer {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10, 31, 61, 0.08);
  }
  .viewer iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 80vh;
    min-height: 640px;
    display: block;
    border: none;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  /* ── Closing ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .closing { background: var(--cream); padding: 80px 32px 100px; }
  .closing p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .closing a {
    color: var(--red);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .intro, .archive, .closing { padding: 56px 24px; }
    .viewer iframe { height: 70vh; min-height: 480px; }
  }
</style>
